<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Let Me Be Known</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Aug 19, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Lord,
</p>

 <p>
Let me be known,
</p>

 <p>
not by what I hate, <br></br>
but by whom I love;
</p>

 <p>
not by whom I exclude, <br></br>
but by whom I include;
</p>

 <p>
not by my enemies, <br></br>
but by my friends;
</p>

 <p>
for an enemy truly loved <br></br>
is but a friend to be.
</p>


 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


